page.title: 07TIME TO ONESELF
page.content: Gardening came top of the list of the hobbies of people interviewed in the Parkwood and Otham areas. Reading was also popular, followed by watching television and knitting. My Normal Weekend : Girl aged 10. Got up at nine oclock played with Angela aged 11 months. Then went on my friends bike his age is 12 his called Antony prior. Then went in and Sarah 9 came out we played sevenseas* then hee and kept an eye on Angela. then I went in for dinner, after dinner we played hee in the woods and then went in at Half past six and at 9.35pm we watch thats life. The best bit was in the Zoo, where they were all singing. now I have to go to bed. *'sevenseas' (sevenses) : a game where players throw a ball up onto a wall but have to bounce it and clap too.
